data.description: Now is your opportunity to live in the Watterson Woods neighborhood in J-Town. This lovely 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home with a large 2 1/2 car attached garage has lots to offer. The first floor features a living room with fireplace, eat in kitchen, laundry area, large master bedroom that offers a Jacuzzi tub and standup shower, full bath, and  two other bedrooms. The basement features a family room and a half bath.  Easy to show.  Call today!
